@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_agwpfs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.sin((v2 + 0.18 - v2 + 0.04)))
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.sin(v2 + 0.39) * tmp))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.abs(0.23))
    v0 = ((0.35 * wp.exp(tmp + 0.34)) + wp.abs(0.67))
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
